Package GUIPackage

package GUIPackage
This package contains all the front-end classes that are used in the game and also builders of the GUIs.
  • Class
    Description
    Builder
    This is an abstract class which implements some basic variables which other Builders will be derived from.
    BuilderInterface
    This interface is used to define the methods every builder will have
    CreatePlan
    In this class where a GUI is created where the user can create a plan for their trip around Hogwarts.
    Menu
    In this class representing a GUI of a menu.
    PlayerSetup
    In this class where a GUI is created where the user can customize their information.
    QuestionsBuilder
    A builder class that is used to build a QuestionsGUI class
    QuestionsGUI
    In this class where a quiz GUI is created.
    StartupGUI
    In this class a login GUI is created.
    StatsBuilder
    A builder class that is used to build a StatsGUI class
    StatsGUI
    In this class where a GUI with statistics is created.
    StoryBuilder
    A builder class that is used to build a StoryGUI class
    StoryGUI
    In this class where a GUI with a story is created.
    TheEndGUI
    In this class where a GUI with "the end" title is created.
